WEBVTT

00:03.400 --> 00:07.079
Indoor theaters and cinemas are still closed due to the coronavirus.

00:07.385 --> 00:11.240
The Tel Aviv municipality is floating a different idea for entertainment.

00:13.533 --> 00:16.374
Whole families, young couples and others in the know...

00:16.468 --> 00:19.555
...taking advantage of the new sail-in floating cinemas...

00:19.694 --> 00:21.026
...in the city's Yarkon Park.

00:21.554 --> 00:24.579
The so-called theater, accommodating up to 200 people,...

00:24.647 --> 00:26.766
...are seated across 70 pedal boats,...

00:27.220 --> 00:29.620
...and each maintaining two meters' distance.

00:29.797 --> 00:31.810
Every day during the last week of August,...

00:31.945 --> 00:33.991
...the city is screening two films on the water...

00:34.109 --> 00:36.516
...at a cost of just 80 shekels per boat.

